#: ../../../topics/scheduler.rst:5
msgid "Scheduler"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/scheduler.rst:9
msgid ""
"The scheduler component receives requests from the :ref:`engine <component-"
"engine>` and stores them into persistent and/or non-persistent data "
"structures. It also gets those requests and feeds them back to the engine "
"when it asks for a next request to be downloaded."
msgstr ""

